  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "=Directions= The Gravhögen sector is a little before Sangis. From Luleå: pass Kalix. About 10 km after Kalix, there is a right turn towards Båtskärsnäs. Pass this turn-off. About 800 m further on, turn left onto a small gravel road (there is a white sign saying “Gravhög”). Follow this road for 1.5 km to the parking area. The boulder is up to the left. The Elljusspåret sector is just before the village of Sangis, 20 km north of Kalix. The boulders lie in an area bounded by the village, road 398, the E4 and the floodlit trail. For parking, turn off the E4 onto road 398. Follow it for about 1 km until a clear-felled area with a floodlit trail appears on the right. Park on a suitable tractor track. =Sectors=",
